en_125291_0	The second son of former President, Yoshitha Rajapaksha who is held at Welikada Prison for CSN fraud, has refused to eat foods provided by jail.
en_125291_1	The sources confirm that permission has been granted for Yoshitha and other suspects who were jailed for the same matter and share the cell with Yoshitha to receive homemade food.
en_125291_2	The Commissioner General of Prisons Department H.N.C. Dhanasinghe told Hiru News that the permission was granted upon a special request made by the detainees.
